{"tid":616410,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"Tripsta 退票 經驗求助","createTime":"2018-04-04T07:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T07:49:42.000Z","uid":83359,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca971455fa882d98952d8e8dd6a3a094919a59e","tid":616410,"uid":83359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"我經[Skyscanner] 係[Tripsta代理網] 訂左 [菲律賓航空] 來回<ins>倫敦</ins>既 機票<br />\n但發覺return日期從JULY選錯左做AUGUST<br />\n<br />\n我想退票, 但GOOGLE完, 發覺好多人都話哩間野伏, 退票改票好難搞<br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過搞哩間野, 可以教下我依家最好要做D乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n我已經send左email過去, 話想退票<br />\n<br />\n我知我今次ON9, 貪平蝕渣米, 自膠左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21a32d5bc22e076b745ada526b8e59e486ca32d","tid":616410,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"聽都未聽過呢間嘢"},{"pid":"628cc6bd59c84730698565b3da8ccff621837d4f","tid":616410,"uid":83359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e21a32d5bc22e076b745ada526b8e59e486ca32d","tid":616410,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"聽都未聽過呢間嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:11:27.000Z","msg":"間野 係網上代理機票<br />\n睇D GOOGLE POST話間野係希臘公司...<br />\nD售後好差, 退票換票好難搞<br />\n果下知今次自己仆街了<br />\n貪少少平, 搞死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6f85eafb5cb3fecd731659a3f41c54cdaaccfc","tid":616410,"uid":83359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T07:19:56.000Z","msg":"push push"},{